Key Match Events: Mitchell Santner scored 36* off 17 balls and took 5 wickets for 59 runs.
Matt Henry took 3 wickets for 40 runs.
Post-Match Reflections: Scott Edwards acknowledged New Zealand's quality bowling attack and emphasized the need for bigger partnerships.
Tom Latham praised the team's batting partnerships and the performance of the bowlers, especially the spinners.
Miscellaneous Highlights: New Zealand consolidated their position at the top of the points table.
Netherlands showed promise in patches but struggled against New Zealand's bowling lineup.
